### Errors

- [Account already linked to different user](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/account_already_linked_to_different_user.md): The account is already linked to a different user.
- [Email doesn't match](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/email_doesn't_match.md): The email doesn't match the email of the account.
- [Email not found](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/email_not_found.md): The provider did not return an email address.
- [Errors](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors.md): Errors that can occur in Better Auth.
- [Invalid callback request](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/invalid_callback_request.md): The callback request is invalid.
- [No callback URL](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/no_callback_url.md): The callback URL was not found in the request.
- [No code](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/no_code.md): The code was not found in the request.
- [OAuth provider not found](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/oauth_provider_not_found.md): The OAuth provider was not found.
- [Signup disabled](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/signup_disabled.md): Signup disabled error
- [State mismatch](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/state_mismatch.md): The state parameter in the request doesn't match the state parameter in the cookie.
- [State not found](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/state_not_found.md): The state parameter was not found in the request.
- [Unable to get user info](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/unable_to_get_user_info.md): The user info was not found in the request.
- [Unable to link account](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/unable_to_link_account.md): The account could not be linked.
- [Unknown error](https://better-auth.com/llms.txt/docs/errors/unknown.md): An unknown error occurred.


